comments: Morris (WAS) legally contests Bridges' (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Craig (PHX) makes clean ball contact to dislodge the rebound away from Gibson (WAS). Any follow-through arm contact after the ball is dislodged is deemed incidental.
After receiving the pass, Kuzma (WAS) avoids stepping out of bounds before his jump shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) and Shamet (PHX) mutually engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Gibson (WAS) legally contests and cleanly blocks Craig's (PHX) layup attempt.
Avdija (WAS) brings his hands toward Craig (PHX) and marginal contact occurs as Avdija releases away to roll toward the basket.
Ayton (PHX) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Avdija (WAS), which affects his play at the basket.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Avdija's (WAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Avdija (WAS) and Ayton (PHX) mutually engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Ayton (PHX) cleanly deflects Kuzma's (WAS) pass at the end of the drive.
Bridges (PHX) moves alongside Morris' (WAS) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt.
Morris (WAS) and Bridges (PHX) come together and incidental contact occurs during their pursuit for the loose ball.
Gibson (WAS) makes clean ball contact to dislodge the rebound away from Bridges (PHX). Any follow-through arm contact after the ball is dislodged is deemed incidental.
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Avdija (WAS).
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Kuzma (WAS).
Gibson (WAS) grasps and releases Ayton's (PHX) jersey as marginal contact occurs when the screen is set.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Avdija's (WAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Lee (PHX) initiates contact with Beal's (WAS) body, which affects his SQBR as he moves up the court.
Kuzma (WAS) legally contests Shamet's (PHX) jump shot attempt.

Avdija (WAS) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Paul (PHX) and is not in a legal guarding position as contact occurs during Paul's (PHX) upward shooting motion. Paul does not abruptly abandon his shot or overtly launch himself into Avdija to draw the contact.
Paul's (PHX) foot comes down in the lane prior to his free throw attempt touching the basket.
Shamet (PHX) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
